{"tid":2455174,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【堅離地傾．沈旭暉】 前高級懲教主任C先生：我再不離開，就會活在思想囚牢（下）","createTime":"2021-03-21T00:54:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T05:23:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"73a98c4b0b4bc4cf236347ab6f8f8886b35aa2df","tid":2455174,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T00:54:22.000Z","msg":"【堅離地傾．沈旭暉 113🇭🇰】<br />\n前高級懲教主任C先生：我再不離開，就會活在思想囚牢（下）<br />\nMar 18, 2021<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZCS-aA9UNUw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZCS-aA9UNUw&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=46604c87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZCS-aA9UNUw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n堅離地球 &middot; 沈旭暉<br />\n195K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n曾任香港懲教處高級懲教主任的C先生，最終決定離開崗位、也離開香港，是因為感覺南深圳化的「新香港」活像一個更大的監獄，比起他管理的監獄更令人窒息，假如再不離開，就活像活在一個思想囚牢。他給予紀律部隊內的有心人，「明天只會更差」，總需要儘快走出comfort zone，下半生才能活得有尊嚴，否則難免被急速改變的新環境完全同化，徹底喪失了自己的靈魂。<br />\n<br />\n▶️ 上篇：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QxQP5...​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQxQP5...%E2%80%8B&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=a461bf3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QxQP5...​</a><br />\n⏺ 這是一場蘇維埃式「Show Trial」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/posts/48332663​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fposts%2F48332663%E2%80%8B&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=9ff1ba2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/posts/48332663​</a><br />\n<br />\nSimon 沈旭暉 堅離地 Social Media ▶<br />\n⏺Patreon: <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/simonshen​​​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fsimonshen%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8B&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=a6d4a724\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreo